      "content": "Wait, \"rebooting\"? I just checked the node status logs on my end and all the nodes are reporting as \"Online\" and \"Active.\" There are no reboot cycles logged in the last 4 hours. If the nodes are online, why isn't the capacity showing up? I'm seeing active CPU utilization on those \"idle\" nodes in the telemetry. Are you sure there isn't some other process hijacking that compute?",
